      "id": "PopularPost229489",
      "post_content": "He's not terrible, just not as good as some of the other Vanguards. You can play him in hellbent decks (easier to reach hellbent when you start 1 down) and decks which use [Necropotence](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Necropotence) or other cards which let you pay life for some advantage. Having a colorless, uncounterable, removal-proof way to pump for that last bit of combat damage is nice too. If it cost less than 1 to 1, it would be too good. As it is now, it is fairly costed, though it would be preferable if it was {1}: +1/+1.",
      "posted_by": "Ideatog",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost229489\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">He's not terrible, just not as good as some of the other Vanguards. You can play him in hellbent decks (easier to reach hellbent when you start 1 down) and decks which use <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Necropotence\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Necropotence\">Necropotence</a> or other cards which let you pay life for some advantage. Having a colorless, uncounterable, removal-proof way to pump for that last bit of combat damage is nice too. If it cost less than 1 to 1, it would be too good. As it is now, it is fairly costed, though it would be preferable if it was {1}: +1/+1.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '229489'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2063\">Ideatog</span>\r\n                                (2/22/2012 10:15:46 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0